text: "Queen Jane Approximately" is a 1966 song by Bob Dylan. It was taken from his sixth studio album Highway 61 Revisited. It was released as a single along with One of Us Must Know (Sooner of Later). It has been covered by The Grateful Dead and The Four Seasons. ==References== Category:1966 songs Category:Bob Dylan songs Category:The Four Seasons (band) songs Category:The Grateful Dead songs Category:Folk rock songs Category:Garage rock songs
